    "created_at": "2015-08-13T21:03:00Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-08-13T21:03:00Z",
    "body": "I agree with @nodakai's assessment that we probably shouldn't be responsible for this, it's pretty common for something else to rewrite `~` as it's going into a program to prevent everyone from reimplementing it, so closing.\n",
